responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D5C2076E4E8A7D26098C7DAD86B67946", "Your discretion is valuable in this matter. Who knew that there are still decent folk among us. You must excuse me for this oversight, since it is such a rare find. Is it true that there exists a code of honor among thieves? ")
